{{#section 'manifest'}}
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/assets/grammar-checker/icon-180.png">
  <link rel="manifest" href="/assets/grammar-checker/manifest.json">
{{/section}}
{{#> layout
  title='Grammar checker for English, German, French, and other languages'
  metaDescription='Perfect your writing with an AI grammar checker that explains errors. Master English, German, French, and more with real-time, educational corrections.'
  url='/grammar.html'
  ogDescription='Perfect your writing with an AI grammar checker that explains errors. Master English, German, French, and more with real-time, educational corrections.'
  navbarAlwaysMurky=true
  navbarClass="mb-4"
  navbarContainerClass="container-md"
  noCta=true
  hidePricing=true
  nonStickyNavbar=true
  disabledAutoTrack=true
}}
  <div class="container-md">
    <div id="grammar-checker" class="pt-3 pb-5"></div>
  </div>
  <div style="background: #f9f9f9;">
    <div class="container-md py-5" style="font-size: 80%">
      <h1 class="h5" style="color: var(--bs-body-color); font-size: 140%">Did I say that correctly?</h1>
      <div class="mb-4">
        If you ask yourself this question, you are probably practicing a foreign language, and you are moving in the right direction, because active language production (speaking and writing) is the fastest catalyst for linguistic growth.
      </div>
      <div class="mb-4">
        However, it is not always possible to have a teacher who can correct every sentence. This free AI grammar checker is designed to act as a personal linguistic coach. It not only corrects mistakes but also explains the reasoning behind corrections, helping learners understand the "why" so they can avoid the same errors in the future.
      </div>
      <div class="mb-4">
        This approach promotes a "production-first" mindset: before reaching for Google Translate or any other automatic translator, try to write the thought in the target language as best you can. Engaging the brain to bridge the gap between thoughts and words is a powerful cognitive exercise intended to positively impact your overall language progress.
      </div>

      {{> social-share
        page="grammar.html"
      }}
    </div>
  </div>
{{/layout}}

